| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | Next.js (React) | High-performance user interface with optimized routing. |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Sleek, modern, and responsive design (works on mobile/desktop). |
